pullrequest.title: Fix camera parameters for submitted models

content.raw:
With our new Robot configuration \(sophisticated\_engineering\_x2\_sensor\_config\_1\) we wanted to create an X2 robot with a Camera with a wider Field of view. Such a camera has already been used in the X2\_Config\_5.

If I do not missunderstand it, this Pull Request will change the field of view of our config. Please do not change this.
